# ⚠️ 5. The “anomaly” channel (critical)

This is where real systems become usable.

```json
{
  "ts":"12:00:09",
  "channel":"anomaly",
  "event":"loop_stall",
  "summary":"Same patch attempted 3 times",
  "severity":"high"
}
```

```json
{
  "ts":"12:00:11",
  "channel":"anomaly",
  "event":"test_flaky",
