# 🧬 6. Higher-order derived logs (your style)

You can layer **semantic transforms**:

```clojure
{:derived
 {:trajectory  ;; evolution of solution
  [:tokenizer-fix → :lexer-fix → :green]

 :confidence-curve
 [0.72 → 0.66 → 0.81]

 :failure-manifold
 {:unicode ["byte/char mismatch"]}}}
```

